---
title: Posh Sausages with Pickled Cucumber, Caramelised Onions & Beans
description: Chef Jesse has created a recipe that is set to bring a bang to your weeknight menu. Our mouthwatering hickory smoked sausages are wrapped in streaky bacon and baked until crispy and golden. They are then topped with sweet caramelised onions and pickled cucumbers, before being served up with homemade smokey baked beans and chunky potato wedges. A guaranteed crowd-pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/posh-dogs-ccc22cdd-27e133f0.jpg
